# Evidence Mapping for Gen-AI Data Privacy & Compliance

## Requirement 1: No sensitive financial, PCI, or PII data used in training/fine-tuning/inference without explicit controls
- **URL**: [Azure OpenAI Data Privacy](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/legal/cognitive-services/openai/data-privacy)
- **Section to Capture**: ‚ÄúCustomer prompts and responses are not used to train, retrain, or improve the models‚Äù
- **Screenshot Instructions**: Open ‚Üí Scroll to section ‚Üí Capture heading and first 6 lines of text  
- **Filename**: `01-data-privacy-no-training.png`

---

## Requirement 2: Explicit encryption controls for data
- **URL**: [Azure AI Security Features](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/ai-services/security-features)
- **Section to Capture**: Section ‚ÄúEncryption‚Äù  
- **Screenshot Instructions**: Open ‚Üí Scroll to section ‚Üí Capture first 6 lines about at-rest and in-transit encryption  
- **Filename**: `02-encryption-controls.png`

---

## Requirement 3: Data retention policy for LLMs
- **URL**: [Azure OpenAI Data Retention](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/legal/cognitive-services/openai/data-privacy#data-retention)
- **Section to Capture**: ‚ÄúData retention‚Äù  
- **Screenshot Instructions**: Scroll to section ‚Üí Capture table with retention period (30 days)  
- **Filename**: `03-data-retention-policy.png`

---

## Requirement 4: Protective measures employed
- **URL**: [Responsible AI and Privacy](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/ai-services/overview-responsible-use)
- **Section to Capture**: ‚ÄúPrivacy and security commitments‚Äù  
- **Screenshot Instructions**: Scroll to section ‚Üí Capture first 2 paragraphs  
- **Filename**: `04-protective-measures.png`

---

## Requirement 5: Written declaration / Compliance statements
- **URL**: [Microsoft Compliance Offerings](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/compliance/regulatory/offering-home)
- **Section to Capture**: Azure compliance offerings  
- **Screenshot Instructions**: Scroll to Azure section ‚Üí Capture list of certifications (ISO, SOC, PCI, HIPAA, etc.)  
- **Filename**: `05-compliance-offerings.png`

---

## Requirement 6: SOC2 Report (independent audit evidence)
- **URL**: [Microsoft Service Trust Portal](https://servicetrust.microsoft.com/)
- **Section to Capture**: Reports > SOC Reports  
- **Screenshot Instructions**: Log in ‚Üí Navigate to SOC Reports ‚Üí Capture SOC 2 Type 2 report availability screen  
- **Filename**: `06-soc2-report.png`

